# IRIS — Tailwind & Visual Identity

## Design Token Reference

### Color Palette
```css
/* globals.css — CSS custom properties */
:root {
  /* Surfaces */
  --color-surface-0: #0A0A0F;   /* Primary background */
  --color-surface-1: #121218;   /* Cards / elevated */
  --color-surface-2: #1A1A24;   /* Hover states / inputs */

  /* Iris purple scale */
  --color-iris-50:  #F0ECFF;
  --color-iris-100: #DDD6FF;
  --color-iris-200: #C2B3FF;
  --color-iris-300: #A48EFF;
  --color-iris-400: #8A6FF8;
  --color-iris-500: #6B4CE6;   /* Primary accent */
  --color-iris-600: #5A3FD3;   /* Buttons / links */
  --color-iris-700: #4A32B8;
  --color-iris-800: #3A2690;
  --color-iris-900: #2A1278;

  /* Gold scale */
  --color-gold-50:  #FFF8E6;
  --color-gold-100: #FEEFC2;
  --color-gold-200: #FDE495;
  --color-gold-300: #FCD468;
  --color-gold-400: #F5C542;   /* Warm gold */
  --color-gold-500: #D4A843;   /* Sacred gold highlight */
  --color-gold-600: #B38A2E;
  --color-gold-700: #8F6D1E;
  --color-gold-800: #6E5014;
  --color-gold-900: #5C4710;

  /* Text */
  --color-text-primary:   #F0ECF9;  /* Warm off-white — ~15:1 contrast */
  --color-text-secondary: #A8A3B8;  /* Muted lavender-gray */
  --color-text-muted:     #6B6780;  /* Captions, timestamps */

  /* Semantic */
  --color-success: #4ADE80;
  --color-error:   #F87171;

  /* Gradients */
  --gradient-sacred-iris: linear-gradient(135deg, #5A3FD3, #7B5EF6, #9B85FF);
  --gradient-iris-to-gold: linear-gradient(135deg, #5A3FD3, #7B5EF6, #D4A843);
  --gradient-night-bloom: linear-gradient(180deg, #0A0A0F 0%, #1A1030 50%, #0A0A0F 100%);

  /* Typography */
  --font-serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
  --font-sans:  'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
}
```

