## Component Patterns

### Cards
```tsx
// Elevated card on surface-1
<div className="bg-[#121218] rounded-2xl border border-iris-900/30 p-6">
  {/* content */}
</div>

// Interactive card with hover
<div className="bg-[#121218] rounded-2xl border border-iris-900/30 p-6
                hover:border-iris-600/50 hover:bg-[#1A1A24]
                transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer">
  {/* content */}
</div>
```

### Buttons
```tsx
// Primary CTA — Sacred Iris gradient
<button className="bg-sacred-iris text-white font-sans font-medium
                   px-8 py-4 rounded-xl
                   hover:opacity-90 active:scale-[0.98]
                   transition-all duration-200">
  Begin Your Journey
</button>

// Secondary — ghost
<button className="border border-iris-600 text-iris-400 font-sans font-medium
                   px-8 py-4 rounded-xl
                   hover:bg-iris-600/10
                   transition-all duration-200">
  Learn More
</button>
```

### Inputs
```tsx
<input
  className="w-full bg-[#1A1A24] border border-iris-900/50 rounded-xl
             px-4 py-3 font-sans text-[#F0ECF9] placeholder:text-[#6B6780]
             focus:outline-none focus:border-iris-500
