### Scroll Animations
```tsx
// Use Intersection Observer for fade-in-up reveals
// Apply 150ms stagger between children
<div className="animate-fade-up" style={{ animationDelay: `${index * 150}ms` }}>
  {children}
</div>
```

## Accessibility
- All text must meet WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 for normal, 3:1 for large).
- `#F0ECF9` on `#0A0A0F` ≈ 15:1 — far exceeds requirements.
- `#A8A3B8` on `#0A0A0F` ≈ 7:1 — passes AA.
- Never use color alone to convey meaning; pair with icons or labels.
- Focus rings: `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-iris-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-[#0A0A0F]`.
